    <abstract>
      <t>WebRTC data channels provide data communication between peers with
   varying reliability and ordering properties.  WebRTC data channels
   traditionally use SCTP layered on top of DTLS over UDP.  This
   document describes how WebRTC data channels can be layered over QUIC.</t>
    </abstract>
